<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>KK FUNDA - Maven Web Application</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #00bcd4, #2196f3);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.3em;
      margin-top: 0;
      animation: slideIn 2.5s ease-in-out;
    }
    .container {
      margin: 50px auto;
      max-width: 800px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .graphics {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    img {
      width: 200px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      margin: 10px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 60px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #e0f7fa;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.95); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    }

    @keyframes slideIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Welcome to KK FUNDA</h1>
  <p>Empowering Java Developers | Maven Web Projects | Spring MVC</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <h2>Project: Maven Web Application</h2>
  <p>This is a sample web application built using Spring MVC, Maven, and Java EE stack.</p>

  <div class="graphics">
    <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2016/11/29/03/53/architecture-1868667_1280.jpg" alt="Modern Office">
    <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2018/01/13/19/39/technology-3085875_1280.jpg" alt="Technology">
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2025 KK FUNDA | Visit us at <a href="http://kkfunda.com" style="color:#fff; text-decoration: underline;">kkfunda.com</a></p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
